OL,3,CThe new campaign using Walkmans and
OL,4,CChopper bikes to raise awareness
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports journalist Tim
OL,7,FScott reports on the new campaign and
OL,8,Fthe benefits of home testing.
OL,10,FA new campaign has employed staples of
OL,11,Fthe 60s and 70s to encourage people to
OL,12,Fget tested for bowel cancer.
OL,14,FThe "Remember when..." campaign from
OL,15,FNorth West Cancer Research calls on
OL,16,Fpeople aged 54 and over to complete
OL,17,Fand return their home bowel cancer
OL,18,Fscreening kits.
