OL,3,CThe new campaign using Walkmans and
OL,4,CChopper bikes to raise awareness
OL,6,FThe campaign features items such as a
OL,7,FWalkman and old-school televisions,
OL,8,Fwith the message: "Remember this? Then
OL,9,Fit's time to complete your bowel
OL,10,Fcancer screening kit."
OL,12,FBowel cancer is the North West's
OL,13,Fsecond biggest cause of cancer deaths,
OL,14,Fwith the region having more cases than
OL,15,Fany other.
OL,17,FDr Dale Vimalachandran, a consultant
OL,18,Fcolorectal surgeon at the Countess of
OL,19,FChester Hospital, says the figures are
OL,20,Fworrying.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
