OL,3,CThe new campaign using Walkmans and
OL,4,CChopper bikes to raise awareness
OL,6,FHe said: "The North West is a
OL,7,Fparticular outlier compared to all
OL,8,Fother regions in the country.
OL,10,F"The number of incidents is the
OL,11,Fhighest, and the outcomes are among
OL,12,Fthe worst across the country. That
OL,13,Fprobably reflects that we're picking
OL,14,Fup the disease at a later stage."
OL,16,FKaren Glover, a teaching assistant
OL,17,Ffrom , is proof that screening works,
OL,18,Fafter a home kit detected her bowel
OL,19,Fcancer before she developed any
OL,20,Fsymptoms.
