OL,3,CThe new campaign using Walkmans and
OL,4,CChopper bikes to raise awareness
OL,6,FShe said: "Doing the test either saved
OL,7,Fmy life, or stopped the cancer from
OL,8,Fspreading.
OL,10,F"I think the cancer would have
OL,11,Fprogressed, it would have spread. I
OL,12,Fhad no symptoms whatsoever to suggest
OL,13,FI should go to the doctors."
OL,15,FThanks to it being caught so early,
OL,16,FKaren is able to live a normal life.
