OL,3,CThe new campaign using Walkmans and
OL,4,CChopper bikes to raise awareness
OL,6,FShe said: "There was no spread of the
OL,7,Fcancer anywhere. Obviously I get
OL,8,Ftested for the next five years, but as
OL,9,Ffar as we're concerned the cancer is
OL,10,Fgone."
OL,12,FIn England, everyone aged 54 to 74 is
OL,13,Fautomatically sent a test kit every
OL,14,Ftwo years, yet new figures show only a
OL,15,Fthird of people send them off.
OL,17,FDr Vimalachandran says the home kits
OL,18,Fcan dramatically effect a patients
OL,19,Fchances.
