OL,3,CThe new campaign using Walkmans and
OL,4,CChopper bikes to raise awareness
OL,6,FHe said: "If we detect the disease at
OL,7,Fan early stage - two things: one, your
OL,8,Foutcome is much better and more
OL,9,Fimportantly we have more treatment
OL,10,Foptions available."
OL,12,FNorth West Cancer Research are also
OL,13,Fproviding information on how to use
OL,14,Fthe test kits.
OL,16,FAs part of their guidance, they said:
OL,17,F"Individuals use the kit to collect a
OL,18,Fsmall sample of poo and send it back
OL,19,Fto a lab to test for signs of cancer."
